'''Cell 12-17''' was a cell located within the [[Salis D'aar Penitentiary]]'s maximum-security section. It was here where [[Malinza Thanas]] was held in [[28 ABY/Legends|28 ABY]] on charges of kidnapping [[Molierre Cundertol]], [[Bakura/Legends|Bakura's]] [[Prime Minister (Bakura)|Prime Minister]] at that time.<ref name="The New Jedi Order: Force Heretic II: Refugee">[[The New Jedi Order: Force Heretic II: Refugee]]</ref>

